---
description: Core stack and coding constraints for app changes
globs:
  - "src/**/*.{ts,tsx}"
alwaysApply: true
---

# Stack Rule

- Keep the existing stack: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind + Framer Motion.
- Prefer extending existing components/hooks/utilities instead of introducing parallel patterns.
- Do not add new runtime dependencies unless they are clearly required by the task.
- Keep files focused and changes minimal; avoid broad refactors in feature tasks.
- Use existing naming and state patterns from nearby modules.
- Update `src/i18n.ts` whenever user-visible strings are changed.
